===生物多样性===
[[File:2020_żubry_03.jpg|thumb]]是波兰的代表性动物之一，集中分布在[[比亞沃維耶扎原始森林|比亞沃維耶扎原始森林]]。]]

波兰森林资源较丰富，森林覆盖率31%，{{link-en|下西里西亚森林|Lower Silesian Forest}}是波兰最大的连续的森林。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://data.worldbank.org/indicator/AG.LND.FRST.ZS?locations=PL|title=Forest area (% of land area) - Poland|work=[[World_Bank|World Bank]]|access-date=2021-04-01}}</ref>境内常见的树种有[[橡树|橡树]]、[[枫树|枫树]]、[[山毛榉|山毛榉]]、[[松树|松树]]、[[云杉|云杉]]、[[冷杉|冷杉]]等。<ref>{{cite book |last=Milewski |first=Wawrzyniec |date=2017 |title=Forests in Poland 2017 |url=https://www.lasy.gov.pl/pl/informacje/publikacje/in-english/forests-in-poland/lasy-w-polsce-2017-en.pdf |location=Warsaw (Warszawa) |publisher=State Forests Information Centre |page=8 |isbn=9788365659231}}</ref>据估计，全国森林中[[松柏門|松柏类]]占69%。<ref>{{cite book |last1=Frouz |first1=Jan |last2=Frouzova |first2=Jaroslava |date=2022 |title=Applied Ecology: How agriculture, forestry and fisheries shape our planet |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=9UpUEAAAQBAJ&dq=most+common+trees++oak+beech+pine++%22poland%22&pg=PA245 |location=Cham |publisher=Springer International Publishing |page=245 |isbn=9783030832254}}</ref>

波兰的动植物与欧洲大陆其他国家相类似。其中，[[欧洲野牛|欧洲野牛]]、[[白鹳|白鹳]]和[[白尾海雕|白尾海雕]]被定为国家的代表性动物，[[虞美人_(植物)|虞美人]]则在民间具有[[国花|国花]]地位。<ref>{{cite web |url=https://culture.pl/en/article/thats-polish-exploring-the-history-of-polands-national-emblems |title=That's Polish: Exploring the History of Poland's National Emblems |last=Aniskiewicz |first=Alena |date=2016 |website=culture.pl |publisher=Adam Mickiewicz Institute |access-date=2022-04-03}}</ref>欧洲野牛、[[欧亚河狸|欧亚河狸]]、[[歐亞猞猁|歐亞猞猁]]、[[灰狼|灰狼]]等动物物种受到国家的重点保护。<ref name="Rocznik" />波兰也是早已灭绝的[[原牛|原牛]]的主要分布地之一，最后一只原牛于1627年死于波兰。<ref>{{cite journal|author=Rokosz, M. |year=1995 |title=History of the Aurochs (''Bos taurus primigenius'') in Poland |journal=Animal Genetics Resources Information |volume=16 |pages=5–12 |doi=10.1017/S1014233900004582 |url=http://agtr.ilri.cgiar.org/agtrweb/Documents/Library/docs/agri16_95.pdf |url-status=dead |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130114152435/http://agtr.ilri.cgiar.org/agtrweb/Documents/Library/docs/agri16_95.pdf |archive-date=2013-01-14}}</ref>森林当中也分布着[[红鹿|红鹿]]、[[欧洲狍|欧洲狍]]、[[野豬|野豬]]等动物。<ref>{{cite book |author1=Reidar Andersen |author2=Marco Apollonio |author3=Rory Putman |author4=Piotr Wawrzyniak |date=2010 |title=European Ungulates and Their Management in the 21st Century |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=-ycg5PtQPugC&dq=boar+deer+poland&pg=PA225 |location=Cambridge |publisher=University Press |pages=223–231 |isbn=9780521760614}}</ref>波兰也是全球[[候鸟|候鸟]]的重要栖息地之一，全球四分之一的白鹳分布于此。<ref>{{cite book |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=dMexywMD_okC&q=%2240%2C000+breeding+pairs%22 |title=Europe: A Continental Overview of Environmental Issues, Volume 4 |publisher=ABC-CLIO World geography |author1=Kevin Hillstrom |author2=Laurie Collier Hillstrom |year=2003 |page=34 |isbn=978-1-57607-686-6}}</ref>

波兰共有23个{{link-en|波兰国家公园|National Parks of Poland|国家公园}}，总面积达{{convert|315100|ha|sqmi}}，占国土面积的1%，其中[[比亞沃維耶扎原始森林|比亞沃維耶扎原始森林]]和[[別什恰迪國家公園|別什恰迪國家公園]]已被列入[[世界遗产|世界遗产]]名录。<ref>{{cite book |last1=Mayer |first1=Marius |date=2019 |title=Cross-Border Tourism in Protected Areas: Potentials, Pitfalls and Perspectives |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=jt-GDwAAQBAJ&dq=23+national+parks+poland&pg=PA115 |location=Cham |publisher=Springer |page=115 |isbn=9783030059606}}</ref>此外，波兰境内还有123个{{link-en|波兰景观公园|Landscape Park (Poland)|景观公园}}以及为数众多的[[自然保护区|自然保护区]]。<ref>{{cite book |last1=Kowalczyk |first1=Barbara |last2=Mikowski |first2=Rafał |last3=Mikowski |first3=Łukasz |date=2019 |title=Environmental law in Poland |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=eo6WDwAAQBAJ&dq=%22123%22+landscape+parks+poland&pg=PT202 |location=Alphen aan den Rijn |publisher=Kluwer Law International |isbn=9789403509501}}</ref>

== 行政區劃 ==
{{main|波蘭行政區劃}}
[[File:POLSKA_mapa_woj_z_powiatami_zh.png|250px]]
[[File:Polandmapzhs.PNG|250px]]
波兰行政区划为[[省_(波兰)|省]]、[[县_(波兰)|县]]、[[乡_(波兰)|乡]]三级制。<ref name="admindiv">{{cite web |url=https://eteryt.stat.gov.pl/eteryt/raporty/WebRaportZestawienie.aspx |title=Liczba jednostek podziału terytorialnego kraju |date=2022 |website=TERYT |publisher=Statistics Poland (Główny Urząd Statystyczny GUS) |access-date=16 March 2022 |language=pl}}</ref>根据2022年数据，波兰全国共有16个省、380个县、2,477个乡。<ref name="admindiv" />波兰的主要城市通常同时具有县和乡的地位。<ref name="admindiv" />省份大多基于{{link-en|波兰历史地区|Polish historical regions|历史地区}}而建立，或因省内主要城市而得名。<ref name="Jordi">{{cite book |last=Martí-Henneberg |first=Jordi |date=2021 |title=European Regions, 1870-2020: A Geographic and Historical Insight into the Process of European Integration. |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=itM-EAAAQBAJ&dq=voivodeships+cities+based+on+historic+regions+of+Poland&pg=PA271 |location=Cham |publisher=Springer International Publishing |pages=259–271 |isbn=9783030615376}}</ref>各省的行政权力由中央指派的{{link-en|省总督 (波兰)|Voivodes of Poland|省总督}}、通过选举产生的{{link-en|省议会 (波兰)|Voivodeship sejmik|省议会}}和由省议会推选产生的{{link-en|省长 (波兰)|Voivodeship marshal|省长}}共享。<ref name="Jordi" />
