== 政治 ==
{{main|波兰政治}}
{{multiple image
 | align = left
 | caption_align = center
 | image1 = Prezydent Rzeczypospolitej Polskiej Andrzej Duda.jpg
 | width1 = 125
 | alt1 = 安杰伊·赛巴斯汀·杜达
 | caption1 = <small>[[波兰总统|总统]]</small><br />[[安杰伊·杜达|安杰伊·杜达]]
 | image2 = Mateusz Morawiecki Prezes Rady Ministrów (cropped).jpg
 | width2 = 138
 | alt2 = 馬特烏什·雅各布·莫拉維茨基
 | caption2 = <small>[[波兰总理|总理]]</small><br />[[馬特烏什·莫拉維茨基|馬特烏什·莫拉維茨基]]
}}
波蘭政府的結構是[[雙首長制|雙首長制]]<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.politico.eu/article/poland-puzzle-election-2019-law-and-justice-party-pis/|title=Europe's Poland puzzle|first=Jan|last=Cienski|date=12 October 2019|website=POLITICO|access-date=2021-07-19|archive-date=2021-12-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211222034228/https://www.politico.eu/article/poland-puzzle-election-2019-law-and-justice-party-pis/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://constitutionnet.org/country/constitutional-history-poland|title=Constitutional history of Poland|website=ConstitutionNet|access-date=2021-07-19|archive-date=2021-12-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211221200318/https://constitutionnet.org/country/constitutional-history-poland|dead-url=no}}</ref>，[[波兰总统|总统]]享有國防和外交權力，行政权则由總統任命的[[波兰总理|總理]]及內閣掌握。總理從[[兩院制|兩院制]]國會的[[众议院_(波兰)|眾議院]]多數黨成員中產生，负责向[[波兰总统|總統]]提名閣員名單，交由總統任命及议会同意。<ref name="Government">{{cite web |url=https://www.gov.pl/web/civilservice/basic-information-about-poland |title=Civil Service; Basic information about Poland |author=Serwis Rzeczypospolitej Polskiej |date=n.d. |website=www.gov.pl |publisher=Government of the Republic of Poland |access-date=2022-03-08 |language=en}}</ref>波蘭總統為[[國家元首|國家元首]]，由公民直選產生，任期5年，可以連任一次，擁有[[解散议会|解散议会]]的權力。<ref>{{cite book |last=Stanisz |first=Piotr |date=2020 |title=Religion and Law in Poland |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=e4MSEAAAQBAJ&q=duda&pg=PT14 |location=Alphen aan den Rijn |publisher=Kluwer Law International |page=13 |isbn=9789403529738 |language=en}}</ref>现任总统为[[安杰伊·杜达|安杰伊·杜达]]，总理为[[馬特烏什·莫拉維茨基|馬特烏什·莫拉維茨基]]。<ref name="cia.gov"/>

[[波蘭議會|波蘭議會]]采用[[两院制|两院制]]，由下院[[众议院_(波兰)|眾議院]]（''{{lang|pl|Sejm}}''，460名成員）和上院[[參議院_(波蘭)|參議院]]（''{{lang|pl|Senat}}''，100名成員）組成。<ref>{{cite book  |date=2021 |title=Foundations of Law: The Polish Perspective |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=zJROEAAAQBAJ&dq=sejm+460++senate+100&pg=PA127 |location=Warszawa (Warsaw) |publisher=Wolters Kluwer Polska |page=127 |isbn=9788382231731 |language=en}}</ref>众议院由[[漢狄法|-{zh-cn:洪德法;zh-tw:頓特法;zh-hk:漢狄法;}-]][[比例代表制|比例代表制]]选举产生<ref>{{cite book |last=Gwiazda |first=Anna |date=2015 |title=Democracy in Poland: Representation, participation, competition and accountability since 1989 |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=VBk-CgAAQBAJ&dq=sejm++d%27Hondt&pg=PA67 |location=Florence |publisher=Taylor and Francis |page=67 |isbn=9781315680118}}</ref>，参议院选举则采用[[简单多数制|简单多数制]]，每一百个选区选出一名参议员<ref name="ConPol">{{cite book |last1=Granat |first1=Mirosław |last2=Granat |first2=Katarzyna |date=2021 |title=The Constitution of Poland: A Contextual Analysis |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=AJzGDwAAQBAJ&dq=poland+senate+first-past-the-post+100&pg=PA52 |location=Oxford |publisher=Hart Publishing |pages=51, 52, 221 |isbn=9781509913947}}</ref>。参议院有权修改或拒绝众议院通过的法规，但众议院可以以多数票推翻参议院的决议。<ref name="Machnikowski">{{cite book |author1=Piotr Machnikowski |author2=Justyna Balcarczyk |author3=Monika Drela |date=2017 |title=Contract law in Poland |chapter-url=https://books.google.com/books?id=OI2WDwAAQBAJ&dq=poland+voting+age+eighteen&pg=PT19 |location=Alphen aan den Rijn |publisher=Kluwer Law International |chapter= Political System (III) |isbn=9789041189332 |oclc=1046634087 |language=en}}</ref>

[[File:Zgromadzenie_Narodowe_4_czerwca_2014_Kancelaria_Senatu_01.JPG|thumb]]]]

議會成員根據省劃直選產生，任期4年<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.electionguide.org/elections/id/3198/|title=IFES Election Guide | Elections: Poland Senate|website=www.electionguide.org|access-date=2021-07-19|archive-date=2021-12-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211221200418/https://www.electionguide.org/elections/id/3198/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。根據1997年生效的現行憲法，除了兩個預留給少數民族政黨的席位（一席予德國裔，另一席予立陶宛裔）外，只有獲得總投票率5％的政黨才能進入众议院。<ref name="ConPol" />只有年满30岁的波兰公民才有资格竞选参议员，而参加总统选举的年龄下限则为35岁。<ref name="Jasinski">{{cite book |last1=Jasiński |first=Wojciech |last2=Kremens |first2=Karolina |date=2019 |title=Criminal law in Poland |chapter-url=https://books.google.com/books?id=DSysDwAAQBAJ&dq=sejm+poland+four+year&pg=PT21 |location=Alphen aan den Rijn |publisher=Kluwer Law International |chapter=Political System and Administrative Structure (IV) |isbn=9789403513249 |language=en}}</ref>

参众两院的成员共同组成[[国民大会_(波兰)|国民大会]]。当新总统就职、对总统的起诉书被递交至{{link-en|国家法庭 (波兰)|State Tribunal (Poland)|国家法庭}}或总统因健康状况无法正常履职时，即组成国民大会。<ref name="Bien">{{cite book |last1=Bień-Kacała |first1=Agnieszka |last2=Młynarska-Sobaczewska |first2=Anna |date=2021 |title=Constitutional law in Poland |chapter-url=https://books.google.com/books?id=lNstEAAAQBAJ&dq=national+assembly+poland++president+oath&pg=PT126 |location=Alphen aan den Rijn |publisher=Kluwer Law International |chapter=The Speaker, Presidium, and Convent of Seniors, Parliamentary Committees (II), s. 281 |isbn=9789403533001 |language=en}}</ref>

===法律===
[[File:Manuscript_of_the_Constitution_of_the_3rd_May_1791.PNG|thumb]]》于1791年获得通过，是欧洲第一部现代意义上的宪法。]]

《[[波兰宪法|波兰共和国宪法]]》是波兰的根本大法。<ref>{{cite book |last1=Kamarad |first1=Ewa |last2=Wysocka-Bar |first2=Anna |date=2020 |title=Private International Law in Poland |chapter-url=https://books.google.com/books?id=f4MSEAAAQBAJ&dq=Supreme+Administrative+Court+supreme+court+constitutional+tribunal+poland&pg=PT16 |location=Alphen aan den Rijn |publisher=Kluwer Law International |chapter=General Introduction, s. 3 |isbn=9789403529615 |language=en}}</ref>现行宪法于1997年4月2日由[[国民大会_(波兰)|国民大会]]通过，其规定波兰为一[[多党制|多党制]][[民主|民主]]国家，人民拥有[[宗教自由|宗教自由]]、[[言论自由|言论自由]]和[[集会自由|集会自由]]，禁止强迫性医学实验、[[酷刑|酷刑]]和[[体罚|体罚]]，并承认家庭的不可侵犯性，以及组织[[工会|工会]]和[[罢工|罢工]]的权利。<ref name="Sejm">{{cite web |url=http://www.sejm.gov.pl/prawo/konst/angielski/kon1.htm |author=Sejm of the Republic of Poland |title=Dziennik Ustaw nr 78: The Constitution of the Republic of Poland |publisher=National Assembly (Zgromadzenie Narodowe) |website=sejm.gov.pl |access-date=2022-03-09 |language=en}}</ref>

波兰的[[司法|司法]]体系由作为国家最高司法机关的{{link-en|波兰最高法院|Supreme Court of Poland|最高法院}}、负责公共行政司法的{{link-en|波兰最高行政法院|Supreme Administrative Court of Poland|最高行政法院}}、普通法院和军事法院构成。<ref name="Kamarad">{{cite book |last1=Kamarad |first1=Ewa |last2=Wysocka-Bar |first2=Anna |date=2020 |title=Private International Law in Poland |chapter-url=https://books.google.com/books?id=f4MSEAAAQBAJ&dq=Supreme+Administrative+Court+supreme+court+constitutional+tribunal+poland&pg=PT16 |location=Alphen aan den Rijn |publisher=Kluwer Law International |chapter=General Introduction, s. 2 |isbn=9789403529615 |language=en}}</ref>最高法院的法官为终身制，由议会任命的独立的{{link-en|国家司法会议 (波兰)|National Council of the Judiciary|國家司法會議}}提名，经議會通過和总统任命後正式上任。<ref name="Jaremba">{{cite book |last=Jaremba |first=Urszula |date=2013 |title=National Judges As EU Law Judges: The Polish Civil Law System |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=CcXMAQAAQBAJ&dq=judges+appointed+by+president+of+poland&pg=PA129 |location=Boston |publisher=Martinus Nijhoff Publishers |pages=126–129 |isbn=9781306070959}}</ref>{{link-en|宪法法庭 (波兰)|Constitutional Tribunal (Poland)|宪法法庭}}和{{link-en|国家法庭 (波兰)|State Tribunal (Poland)|国家法庭}}是独立的司法机构，它们负责裁定国家最高领导人的宪法责任，并监督成文法的遵守情况，从而保护宪法。<ref name="Jaremba" />众议院经参议院批准，任命一名[[申訴專員|申訴專員]]，任期五年，负责维护社会正义。<ref name="ConPol" />

波兰治安良好，2018年谋杀率为每10万人中仅有0.7人被谋杀<ref name="hdr.undp.org">{{cite web |url=http://hdr.undp.org/en/countries/profiles/POL |title=Human Development Indicators – Poland |date=2020 |website=Human Development Reports |publisher=United Nations Development Programme |access-date=2020-12-16}}</ref>，性犯罪和暴力犯罪的发生率也很低<ref>{{cite web |url=https://dataunodc.un.org/content/data/homicide/homicide-rate |title=Victims of intentional homicide 1990–2018 – Poland |date=2018 |website=Data UNODC |publisher=United Nations Office on Drugs and Crime |access-date=2020-12-16}}</ref>。然而，波兰对[[堕胎|堕胎]]的限制严格，只有在被强奸、乱伦或妇女生命受到威胁的情况下才允许堕胎， 而胎儿的先天性疾病和死产则不在法律允许范围内，因此迫使一些妇女到国外寻求堕胎。<ref>{{cite book |author1=Zsuzsa Csergo |author2=Daina Stukuls Eglitis |author3=Paula M Pickering |date=2021 |title=Central and East European Politics: Changes and Challenges |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=ibgzEAAAQBAJ&dq=poland+abortion+rape+incest+danger&pg=PA168 |location=Lanham, Maryland |publisher=Rowman & Littlefield |page=168 |isbn=9781538142790}}</ref>

波兰历史上最重要的法律文件是1791年5月3日通过的《[[五三宪法|五三宪法]]》，这部宪法旨在纠正[[波兰立陶宛联邦|波兰立陶宛联邦]]及其[[贵族民主制|贵族民主制]]长期存在的政治缺陷，是欧洲第一部现代意义上的宪法，并对后世世界范围内的民主运动产生了深远影响。<ref name="Davies 699">{{cite book|url=https://archive.org/details/europehistory00davi_0|url-access=registration|first=Norman|last=Davies|title=Europe: A History|year=1996|publisher=Oxford University Press|page=[https://archive.org/details/europehistory00davi_0/page/699 699]|isbn=978-0-19-820171-7 |via=Internet Archive}}</ref><ref>{{cite book |url=https://archive.org/details/europehistory00davi_0 |url-access=registration |author=Norman Davies |title=Europe: A History |year=1996 |publisher=Oxford University Press |page=[https://archive.org/details/europehistory00davi_0/page/699 699] |isbn=978-0-19-820171-7}}</ref><ref>{{cite book |last=Gierowski |first=Józef Andrzej |author-link=Józef Andrzej Gierowski |title=Historia Polski, 1505–1764 |language=pl |trans-title=History of Poland, 1505–1764 |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=IBNjywAACAAJ |access-date=26 October 2014| year=1986| publisher=Państwowe Wydawnictwo Naukowe |isbn=978-83-01-03732-1 |page=251}}</ref>1918年，[[波兰第二共和国|波兰第二共和国]]修法允许妇女投票，成为最早实行[[女性參政權|妇女普选权]]的国家之一。<ref>{{cite book |last=Berglund |first=Sten |date=2006 |title=The Making of the European Union: Foundations, Institutions and Future Trends |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=DOAEFRDAEi4C&dq=%22poland%22+one+of+the+first+countries+to+women%27s+suffrage+1918&pg=PA46 |location=Cheltenham |publisher=Edward Elgar Publishing Press |page=46 |isbn=9781845420253}}</ref>

=== 外交 ===
{{main|波兰外交}}
[[File:Ministerstwo_Spraw_Zagraniczych_al._Szucha_23.JPG|thumb]]]]
波兰是一个[[中等强国|中等强国]]，自2004年加入[[歐盟|歐盟]]以來，波蘭歷屆政府積極參與歐洲和國際事務，被視為欧洲的新興強權，并正逐渐向[[地域大国|地域大国]]转型。<ref>{{cite journal |last=Glazebrook |first=G. deT. |title=The Middle Powers in the United Nations System |url=https://archive.org/details/sim_international-organization_1947-06_1_2/page/307 |journal=[[International_Organization_(journal)|International Organization]] |volume=1 |number=2 |date=June 1947 |pages=307–315 |publisher=[[University_of_Wisconsin_Press|University of Wisconsin Press]] |doi=10.1017/S0020818300006081 |jstor=2703870}}</ref><ref>{{cite book |last=Bindi |first=Federiga |date=2019 |title=Europe and America: the end of the transatlantic relationship? |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=FnR0DwAAQBAJ&dq=poland+is+becoming+a+%22regional+power%22&pg=PA6 |location=Washington, D.C. |publisher=Brookings Institution Press |page=6 |isbn=9780815732815}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://geopoliticalfutures.com/polands-rising-leadership-position/|title=Poland's Rising Leadership Position|website=Geopolitical Futures|access-date=2021-07-19|archive-date=2021-12-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211223070312/https://geopoliticalfutures.com/polands-rising-leadership-position/|dead-url=no}}</ref>波蘭是歐盟人口第五多的成員國，截至2020年，在歐洲議會中共有52名代表。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.europarl.europa.eu/news/en/press-room/20200130IPR71407/redistribution-of-seats-in-the-european-parliament-after-brexit|title=Redistribution of seats in the European Parliament after Brexit | News | European Parliament|date=31 January 2020|website=www.europarl.europa.eu|access-date=2021-07-19|archive-date=2021-01-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210118115313/https://www.europarl.europa.eu/news/en/press-room/20200130IPR71407/redistribution-of-seats-in-the-european-parliament-after-brexit|dead-url=no}}</ref>{{link-en|欧洲边境与海岸警卫队|Frontex}}以及[[欧安组织|欧安组织]]{{link-en|欧安组织民主与人权办公室|Office for Democratic Institutions and Human Rights|民主与人权办公室}}均位于[[华沙|华沙]]。<ref>{{cite book |last1=De Londras |first1=Fiona |last2=Doody |first2=Josephine |date=2015 |title=The impact, legitimacy and effectiveness of EU counter-terrorism |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=AYMGCAAAQBAJ&dq=frontex+warsaw+based&pg=PA58 |location=London |publisher=Routledge, Taylor & Francis Group |page=58 |isbn=9781138097957}}</ref><ref>{{cite book |last1=Weissbrodt |first1=David S. |last2=Vega |first2=Connie |orig-date=2007 |date=2010 |title=International Human Rights Law: An Introduction |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=RaU1U-4gBCkC&dq=ODIHR+headquartered+warsaw&pg=PA324 |location=Philadelphia |publisher=University of Pennsylvania Press |page=324 |isbn=9780812221206}}</ref>除此之外，波蘭也是[[聯合國|聯合國]]、[[北約|北約]]、[[世界貿易組織|世界貿易組織]]、[[經濟合作與發展組織|經濟合作與發展組織]]等重要国际组织的成員。

近年来，波蘭大力加強與[[西方世界|西方世界]]，尤其是[[美國|美國]]的關係，從而成為美國在歐洲最親密的盟友与战略伙伴之一。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.state.gov/u-s-relations-with-poland/|title=U.S. Relations With Poland|access-date=2021-07-19|archive-date=2020-11-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201117043458/https://www.state.gov/u-s-relations-with-poland/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.ips-journal.eu/regions/global/the-future-of-the-polish-american-special-relationship-4577/|title=The future of the Polish-American 'special relationship'|website=www.ips-journal.eu|access-date=2021-07-19|archive-date=2021-12-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211223070324/https://www.ips-journal.eu/regions/global/the-future-of-the-polish-american-special-relationship-4577/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite book |last=Deni |first=John R. |date=2021 |title=Coalition of the unwilling and unable: European realignment and the future of American geopolitics |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=B6QQEAAAQBAJ&dq=decades+closest+allies+us+poland&pg=PA148 |location=Michigan |publisher=University of Michigan Press |page=148 |isbn=9780472128792}}</ref> 传统上，[[匈牙利－波兰关系|波兰与匈牙利关系密切]]，2007年，波匈两国议会通过联合声明，将3月23日定为“波匈友谊日”。<ref>{{cite book |last=Suszycki |first=Andrzej Marcin |date=2021 |title=Nationalism in Contemporary Europe: Concept, Boundaries and Forms |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=DDQxEAAAQBAJ&dq=poland+hungary+friendship+march+23&pg=PA193 |location=Zürich |publisher=LIT |page=193 |isbn=9783643911025}}</ref>

===执法与应急服务===
[[File:Mercedes-Benz_Sprinter_Policja_Krakow_G719.JPG|thumb]]

波兰的执法由隶属于{{link-en|波兰内政部|Ministry of Interior and Administration (Poland)|内政部}}之下的几大执法机构——负责调查犯罪或违法行为的{{link-en|国家警察 (波兰)|Policja|国家警察}}、负责维护公共秩序的{{link-en|城市卫队 (波兰)|City Guard (Poland)|城市卫队}}以及负责边防的{{link-en|边境卫队 (波兰)|Border Guard (Poland)|边境卫队}}等负责。<ref name="auto3">{{cite web|url=https://www.bbn.gov.pl/pl/bezpieczenstwo-narodowe/system-bezpieczenstwa-n/bezpieczenstwo-publiczn/5977,Potencjal-ochronny.html|title=Potencjał ochronny|first=Biuro Bezpieczeństwa|last=Narodowego|website=Biuro Bezpieczeństwa Narodowego}}</ref>私人保安公司也很常见，但它们并不具备逮捕或拘留嫌疑人的权力。<ref name="auto3"/><ref>{{cite web|url=https://gazetawroclawska.pl/klient-kontra-ochrona-sklepu-czy-moga-nas-zatrzymac-przeszukac-legitymowac/ar/13722260|title=Klient kontra ochrona sklepu. Czy mogą nas zatrzymać, przeszukać, legitymować?|first=Marcin|last=Rybak|date=2018-12-06|website=Gazeta Wrocławska}}</ref>城市卫队主要由省、地区或市议会领导，未经上级批准不得携带枪支。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://sip.lex.pl/akty-prawne/dzu-dziennik-ustaw/straze-gminne-16798909/roz-3#:~:text=30%20ustawy%20z%20dnia%2021,r.%20o%20broni%20i%20amunicji.&text=Stra%C5%BCnik%2C%20o%20kt%C3%B3rym%20mowa%20w,11%20pkt%205%20i%209.|title = Rozdział 3 - Uprawnienia i obowiązki strażników - Straże gminne. - Dz.U.2019.1795 t.j.}}</ref>执法人员定期在大城市或较小的郊区进行巡逻。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://doba.pl/ddz/artykul/policja-o-zwierzchnictwie-nad-straza-miejska-w-powiecie-dzierzoniowskim-/44242/15/noa123|title=Policja o zwierzchnictwie nad Strażą Miejską w powiecie dzierżoniowskim|website=doba.pl}}</ref>

{{link-en|波兰国内安全局|Internal Security Agency (Poland)}}是负责保卫波兰[[国家安全|国家安全]]的[[反情报|反情报]]机构，而{{link-en|外国情报局|Foreign Intelligence Agency}}则负责识别外部威胁、获取境外情报，二者共同构成了波兰的情报系统。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://aw.gov.pl/rekrutacja/|title=Agencja Wywiadu|website=aw.gov.pl}}</ref>{{link-en|中央警察调查局|Centralne Biuro Śledcze Policji}}和{{link-en|中央反腐局|Central Anticorruption Bureau}}则分别负责国家的反有组织犯罪和反腐败工作。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://cba.gov.pl/pl/aktualnosci|title=Aktualności|first=Centralne Biuro|last=Antykorupcyjne|website=Centralne Biuro Antykorupcyjne}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://bip.cbsp.policja.gov.pl/CBS/status-prawny-1/8969,Status-prawny.html|title=Status prawny|first=J. S. K.|last=Internet|website=Centralne Biuro Śledcze Policji}}</ref>

波兰的应急服务系统由{{link-en|波兰的医疗急救服务|Emergency medical services in Poland|急救体系}}、{{link-en|国家消防局 (波兰)|State Fire Service|国家消防局}}以及[[波兰军队|波军]]中的[[搜救|搜救]]单位组成。波兰的急救服务由地方政府运营<ref>{{cite web|url=http://orka.sejm.gov.pl/proc4.nsf/projekty/2947_p.htm|title=Projekt ustawy o krajowym systemie ratowniczym|website=orka.sejm.gov.pl}}</ref>，同时隶属于直属中央的国家医疗紧急服务中心（{{lang-pl|Państwowe Ratownictwo Medyczne}}）。<ref>{{cite web|title=Ustawa z dnia 25 lipca 2001 r. o Państwowym Ratownictwie Medycznym.|url=http://isap.sejm.gov.pl/isap.nsf/DocDetails.xsp?id=WDU20011131207|access-date=2021-08-10|website=isap.sejm.gov.pl}}</ref>

==軍事==
{{main|波蘭軍事}}
[[File:F-16_Jastrząb_(48).jpg|thumb]]]]
[[波蘭共和國軍|波蘭共和國軍]]是波兰主要的军事力量，由五大兵種——[[波蘭陸軍|陸軍]]、[[波蘭海軍|海軍]]、[[波兰空军|空軍]]、{{link-en|波兰特种部队|Polish Special Forces|特种部队}}和{{link-en|波兰领土防卫部队|Territorial Defence Force (Poland)|領土防衛部隊}}组成，隸屬於{{link-en|波蘭國防部|Ministry of National Defence (Poland)}}。<ref name="PAF">{{cite book |last1=Mihalčová |first1=Bohuslava  |last2=Szaryszová |first2=Petra |last3=Štofová |first3=Lenka  |last4=Pružinský |first4=Michal |last5=Gontkovičová |first5=Barbora |date=2019 |orig-date=2018 |title=Production Management and Business Development : Proceedings of the 6th Annual International Scientific Conference on Marketing Management, Trade, Financial and Social Aspects of Business. |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=goqADwAAQBAJ&dq=poland+armed+forces+territorial+defense+navy+land+forces%2C+air+force&pg=PA174 |location=Boca Raton |publisher=CRC Press |pages=174–175 |isbn=9780429468667}}</ref>和平時期，總統擔任三军總司令，並有權提名軍官、國防部長和參謀長。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://sip.lex.pl/akty-prawne/dzu-dziennik-ustaw/konstytucja-rzeczypospolitej-polskiej-16798613/art-134|title=ZAKOŃCZENIE I UMORZENIE POSTĘPOWANIA UPADŁOŚCIOWEGO ORAZ ICH SKUTKI – Tytuł 9 – Prawo upadłościowe.|first=Wolters|last=Kluwer|website=OpenLEX|access-date=2021-07-19|archive-date=2021-12-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211212223009/https://sip.lex.pl/akty-prawne/dzu-dziennik-ustaw/konstytucja-rzeczypospolitej-polskiej-16798613/art-134|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.wojsko-polskie.pl/prezydent-rp/|title=Prezydent RP|website=Wojsko-Polskie.pl|access-date=2021-07-19|archive-date=2021-12-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211228224542/https://www.wojsko-polskie.pl/prezydent-rp/|dead-url=no}}</ref>每年8月15日是波兰的{{link-en|武装部队日 (波兰)|Armed Forces Day (Poland)|武装部队日}}。<ref>{{cite book |last=Zalewski |first=Jerzy |date=2002 |title=Wojsko Polskie w przemianach ustrojowych 1989-2001 |url=https://www.google.com.au/books/edition/Wojsko_Polskie_w_przemianach_ustrojowych/ML4hAQAAIAAJ?hl=en&gbpv=0&bsq=%C5%9Bwi%C4%99to%20wojska%20polskiego%2015%20sierpnia%20sejm |location=Warszawa (Warsaw) |publisher=Elipsa |page=131 |isbn=978-83-7151-494-4 |language=pl}}</ref>截至2022年，波蘭共和國軍共有114,050名现役士兵，另有75,400人在{{link-en|波兰宪兵|Military Gendarmerie (Poland)|宪兵部队}}和[[准军事组织|准军事组织]]服役。<ref name="WOJ">{{cite book |author=International Institute for Strategic Studies (IISS) |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=ENljEAAAQBAJ&dq=The+Military+Balance+2021+poland&pg=PA134 |title=The Military Balance 2022 |year=2022 |location=Milton |publisher=Routledge |pages=134–137 |isbn=9781000619720}}</ref>2022年，波兰军费约为145亿美元，相当于其GDP的2%。<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.janes.com/defence-news/news-detail/poland-to-increase-defence-spending-to-3-of-gdp-from-2023 |title=Poland to increase defence spending to 3% of GDP from 2023 |last=Popescu |first=Ana-Roxana |date=2022 |website=Janes |publisher=Montagu Private Equity |access-date=24 March 2022}}</ref>根据[[斯德哥尔摩国际和平研究所|斯德哥尔摩国际和平研究所]]的数据，2020年波兰共向国外出口了价值4.87亿欧元的武器装备。<ref>{{cite report |author=Government of Poland |date=2019 |title=Eksport uzbrojenia i sprzętu wojskowego Polski |url=https://www.sipri.org/sites/default/files/2020-07/poland_2018.pdf |location=Warszawa (Warsaw) |publisher=Ministerstwo Spraw Zagranicznych MSZ (Ministry of Foreign Affairs) |page=4 |access-date=2022-03-24}}</ref>

波兰的国家安全总体目标是进一步融入北约和欧盟的国防、经济和政治体系。<ref name="mil">{{cite web|url = http://www.wp.mil.pl/pliki/File/zalaczniki_do_stron/SBN_RP.pdf|title = Strategia Bezpieczeństwa Narodowego RP|work = www.wp.mil.pl|access-date = 2008-09-28|language = pl|url-status=dead|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20081001155817/http://www.wp.mil.pl/pliki/File/zalaczniki_do_stron/SBN_RP.pdf|archive-date = 2008-10-01|df = dmy-all}}</ref>波兰原实行[[征兵制|征兵制]]，适龄符合条件的男子均需要服役9个月，但这一制度在2008年被废除。<ref name="Poland ends army conscription">{{cite news|last=Day|first=Matthew|url=https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/europe/poland/2505447/Poland-ends-army-conscription.html |archive-url=https://ghostarchive.org/archive/20220110/https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/europe/poland/2505447/Poland-ends-army-conscription.html |archive-date=2022-01-10|url-access=subscription |url-status=live|title=Poland ends army conscription|newspaper=Telegraph|date=2008-08-05|access-date=28 July 2011|location=London}}{{cbignore}}</ref>波兰的军事学说侧重防御，与大多数北约成员国类似，并积极参加北约举行的[[军事演习|军事演习]]。<ref name="WOJ" />自1953年以来，波兰曾多次参与国际[[维和行动|维和行动]]。<ref>{{cite book |last=Zięba |first=Ryszard |date=2020 |title=Poland's Foreign and Security Policy: Problems of Compatibility with the Changing International Order |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=Mc-8DwAAQBAJ&dq=poland+contributor+peacekeeping+missions+middle+east&pg=PA226 |location=Cham |publisher=Springer International Publishing |pages=226–229 |isbn=9783030306977}}</ref>目前，波兰在[[中东|中东]]、[[非洲|非洲]]、[[波罗的海三国|波罗的海三国]]、[[东南欧|东南欧]]等地有驻军。<ref name="WOJ" />

== 经济 ==
